---
title: Veggie Thai Yellow Curry with Brown Rice & Roasted Peanuts
description: Enjoy a bowl of creamy and rich Thai curry, loaded with colourful veggies and aromatic spices. With a sprinkling of roasted peanuts to finish it all off, this delicious meal will beat your local takeaway joint!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-coconut-curry-with-rice-d0b7eb6a.jpg
